Zeng Gang told the reporters that the number of non-performing assets is increasing at present.

83
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,959
To maximize the value of the assets...

84
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:47,970
After reading so many books, do you know what a non-performing asset is?

85
00:05:47,970 --> 00:05:51,340
Based on current observation, the non-performing assets industry is
rich in resources.

86
00:05:51,340 --> 00:05:53,199
It is a broad concept.

87
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:55,860
It's about bad debt in a balance sheet account.

88
00:05:55,860 --> 00:06:00,520
It mainly includes but is not limited to non-performing assets of the banks, government,

89
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:03,079
capitals, securities, insurance,

90
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:06,240
and non-performing assets of businesses.

91
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,519
But I still don't get it.

92
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:11,060
Since this is the case, how can it be a resource?

93
00:06:11,060 --> 00:06:13,180
It's hard to explain this.

94
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:15,539
The thing is, when it comes to non-performing assets,

95
00:06:15,539 --> 00:06:19,920
