The property management just called, saying the air-conditioner in your room will take one month for repair.

112
00:09:33,649 --> 00:09:36,170
There's another room there. The air-conditioner works.

113
00:09:36,170 --> 00:09:38,040
Stay there for now.

114
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,710
Here are the keys.

115
