Eat quickly. You're going to be late for work.

117
00:09:49,439 --> 00:09:50,610
What's the hurry.

118
00:09:50,610 --> 00:09:54,660
It only takes half an hour by car. I can arrive 20 minutes earlier.

119
00:09:54,660 --> 00:09:57,480
I'm not driving you there.

120
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,950
You...

