127
00:11:09,549 --> 00:11:10,939
Stop pushing me!

128
00:11:10,939 --> 00:11:12,839
I'm not getting on this bus!

129
00:11:12,839 --> 00:11:14,910
It's not the bus I'm waiting for!

130
