143
00:12:26,299 --> 00:12:30,309
Anyone who comes late this month can start following this rule.

144
00:12:31,540 --> 00:12:34,590
Director Song, you should set an example.

145
00:12:34,590 --> 00:12:36,210
You did this on purpose.

146
00:12:36,210 --> 00:12:39,400
I won't do it. You can deduct my pay.

147
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:43,140
You can disregard the money and the rules.

148
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:45,300
Of course, you're the CEO.

149
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:49,020
But before that, you can see what they think.

150
00:12:50,060 --> 00:12:50,909
Watch them.

151
00:12:50,909 --> 00:12:53,050
Okay.

152
00:12:53,050 --> 00:12:55,729
- What is wrong with him?
- So, what's your decision?

153
00:12:55,729 --> 00:12:58,019
It's pretty embarrassing.

154
