But when I see my shopping cart,

155
00:13:00,300 --> 00:13:03,659
I think there's no point saving my face.

156
00:13:03,659 --> 00:13:06,079
It's more practical to get a few lipsticks.

157
00:13:06,079 --> 00:13:10,139
You're right. Didn't some people make a scene at the company's entrance before?

158
00:13:10,139 --> 00:13:13,520
Yes. I was late a few times because of them.

159
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:16,169
It's all good now. Our pay won't be deducted anymore.

160
00:13:16,169 --> 00:13:18,939
I no longer have to push myself to death for that one minute.

161
00:13:18,939 --> 00:13:23,009
Just the other day, I was almost squashed to death in the lift.

162
00:13:23,009 --> 00:13:26,540
Since you've decided, let's not waste time.

163
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:27,899
Please line up here.

164
00:13:27,899 --> 00:13:29,139
- Come on.
- Let's go.

165
00:13:29,139 --> 00:13:30,299
Director Song, what about you?

166
00:13:30,299 --> 00:13:32,260
I'll join them.

167
00:13:32,260 --> 00:13:34,540
Okay, let's get into position.

168
00:13:34,540 --> 00:13:36,059
I'll start recording.

169
00:13:36,059 --> 00:13:37,670
Are you ready?

170
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:39,299
We'll start if you're ready.

171
00:13:39,299 --> 00:13:42,560
Three. Two. One. Action!

172
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:44,160
One!

173
00:13:46,570 --> 00:13:48,580
Two!

174
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:50,179
That's the spirit.

175
00:13:50,179 --> 00:13:51,370
A close-up on you, Director Song.

176
00:13:51,370 --> 00:13:53,120
- Zheng Hao!
- Three!

177
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:54,810
What are you doing?

178
00:13:56,060 --> 00:13:58,900
Director Qin, it's a new regulation.

179
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:03,639
You're the general manager. You're different from other employees.

180
00:14:03,639 --> 00:14:05,709
Some incidents will inevitably delay you from coming to work on time.

181
00:14:05,709 --> 00:14:07,809
- Did Su Zhinian force you do this?
- No.

182
00:14:07,809 --> 00:14:10,040
- He—
- I'll talk to him.

183
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:15,179
Do we still need to do it?

184
00:14:15,179 --> 00:14:19,209
Before a new rule is announced, we'll continue with the existing rule.

185
00:14:19,209 --> 00:14:21,060
Continue.

186
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:29,910
Director Su, Qingchun is Huateng Land's CEO.

187
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:33,139
You made her do squats in front of so many people. It will affect her negatively.

188
00:14:33,139 --> 00:14:35,940
How can she manage the company with others' respect in the future?

189
00:14:39,540 --> 00:14:43,960
If an employer can't even be punctual,

190
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,540
how can she earn others' respect?

191
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:47,140
She was only one minute late.

192
00:14:47,140 --> 00:14:50,419
One minute is enough for a public company's stock to reach its bottom limit

193
00:14:50,419 --> 00:14:52,780
and make those who bought the stock go bankrupt.

194
00:14:52,780 --> 00:14:57,400
There are even more serious cases. Do you want me to tell you one by one?

195
00:15:02,300 --> 00:15:05,110
Don't you think you're being too harsh on her?

196
00:15:05,110 --> 00:15:08,310
She's no longer the high school student you tutored.

197
00:15:09,180 --> 00:15:12,639
Director Qin, may I know if you work

198
00:15:12,639 --> 00:15:14,790
while reporting to your subordinate?

199
00:15:17,940 --> 00:15:21,690
So do I need to work while reporting to you?

200
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:28,909
Do you think coming to work on time can solve Huateng's current crisis?

201
00:15:28,909 --> 00:15:30,350
Of course, not.

202
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:33,809
So I'll be very busy these days.

203
00:15:33,809 --> 00:15:37,679
Also, please don't waste my time on something like this.

204
00:15:37,679 --> 00:15:39,519
Just do your job.

205
00:15:39,519 --> 00:15:41,540
I'm doing this for Qingchun's sake.

206
00:15:41,540 --> 00:15:43,679
I don't care why you invested in Huateng Land.

207
00:15:43,679 --> 00:15:48,710
But as long as I'm around, I won't let you hurt Qingchun again.

208
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:54,160
Director Qin.

209
00:15:57,200 --> 00:16:01,469
Directgor Su, We've bid the Song's family house. Miss Song can move in anytime.

210
00:16:01,469 --> 00:16:03,059
Don't tell her first.

211
00:16:03,059 --> 00:16:07,759
Also, put back the seal, and leave everything in its original state.

212
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:10,659
Today is Zijin Harbor launch.

213
00:16:10,659 --> 00:16:13,060
Tell her to do market research right away.

214
00:16:13,060 --> 00:16:15,499
Submit the report to me when she comes to work tomorrow.

215
00:16:15,499 --> 00:16:17,040
Okay.

216
00:16:20,650 --> 00:16:22,690
[Alexander Brand]

217
00:16:59,900 --> 00:17:02,670
- I'm sorry.
- Young lass, why don't you watch where you're going?

218
00:17:02,670 --> 00:17:05,329
- I'm sorry.
-You'll have to pay for this.

219
00:17:07,010 --> 00:17:08,579
You must compensate me!

220
00:17:08,579 --> 00:17:10,440
Compensate you?

221
00:17:11,450 --> 00:17:15,389
My wife prepared this jade as a dowry for my daughter.

222
00:17:15,389 --> 00:17:17,950
It's a family heirloom that can't be bought anywhere!

223
00:17:17,950 --> 00:17:21,139
It's broken into pieces now! You must pay for this jade!

224
00:17:21,139 --> 00:17:22,429
You must pay.

225
00:17:22,429 --> 00:17:25,279
Excuse me. I didn't even come into contact with you just now.

226
00:17:25,279 --> 00:17:27,239
Moreover, we don't even know where this jade comes from.

227
00:17:27,239 --> 00:17:28,529
No contact?

228
00:17:28,529 --> 00:17:31,289
Hey, you didn't watch where you were going.

229
00:17:31,289 --> 00:17:35,540
You broke my jade into pieces. Yet you refused to admit it!

230
00:17:35,540 --> 00:17:39,600
Just look at her. What kind of attitude is this?

231
00:17:40,450 --> 00:17:43,289
I'm only treating you the way you deserve.

232
00:17:43,289 --> 00:17:45,669
I think you were faking it to extort me!

233
00:17:45,669 --> 00:17:47,139
What did you say?

234
00:17:47,139 --> 00:17:49,629
You broke my jade into pieces, and you're saying I'm trying to extort you?

235
00:17:49,629 --> 00:17:51,139
Officer, how about this?

236
00:17:51,139 --> 00:17:54,349
We can check the surveillance or wait for my lawyer friend to come.

237
00:17:54,349 --> 00:17:56,389
Then you can follow the procedure.

238
00:17:56,389 --> 00:17:57,759
Don't try to scare me.

239
00:17:57,759 --> 00:17:59,579
Aren't you lying too?

240
00:17:59,579 --> 00:18:01,919
Enough. Say no more.

241
00:18:01,919 --> 00:18:04,630
After the CCTV footage is here, everything will be clear.

242
00:18:04,630 --> 00:18:07,979
You two, write down the contact number of the people we can contact.

243
00:18:08,820 --> 00:18:10,490
Write it.

244
00:18:36,900 --> 00:18:38,349
Hello, Director Su.

245
00:18:38,349 --> 00:18:40,099
Where's Song Qingchun?

246
00:18:40,099 --> 00:18:44,569
I told her to do market research, not shopping. Tell her to come out after she's done.

247
00:18:44,569 --> 00:18:49,099
She has finished the market research. But she's being extorted and is currently trying to settle it.

248
00:18:55,490 --> 00:18:57,339
Is your friend's name Qin Yinan?

249
00:18:57,339 --> 00:18:58,660
